Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, tako sam srećna!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.70,0:00:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.41,SFX-BrownWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(232,192)\fad(200,0)}Ova kutija...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.66,0:00:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.45,0:00:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Da nisi ti napravio ovo?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.91,0:00:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neverovatno, primetila je samo na osnovu kutije?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.04,0:00:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da vidim!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Smem li da otvorim?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.54,0:00:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.58,0:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pekao sam ih tačno koliko je pisalo, ali su izgledali bledo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.80,0:00:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa sam ih ostavio još,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.96,0:00:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,i delovali su okej,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.63,0:00:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,ali su ubrzo pocrneli i sad su nekako tvrdi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.43,0:00:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne mogu da ih pojedem! Previše su mi dragoceni!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.81,0:00:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali želim da ih probam!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.27,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Smem li?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.48,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.31,0:00:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisu tvrdi?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.65,0:00:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Super su ukusni!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeo?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.53,0:00:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, razmišljao sam kako je baš lepo kada neko pojede nešto što si spremio.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.45,0:01:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Da devojka koju voliš srećno pojede ono što si spremio...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.20,0:01:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja se uvek tako osećam!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tako znači.
