Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.55,Title1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(644,125.333)}Pismo i ja
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesu li joj se svideli kolači?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.26,SFX-BlackWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1108,298)\fad(0,650)}Hvala na pomoći
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nadam se da ćeš i ti naći neku koja ti se sviđa uskoro.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.64,0:02:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I nadam se da će ta devojka voleti domaće pirinčane krekere.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Krekere?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislio sam kolače!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ako bude to devojka koja može da se nasmeši,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.90,SFX-BlackWhite,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1104,43.333)}Baš si omašio...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,137)\i1}dok jede kolače tvrde kao pirinčane krekere...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.12,0:03:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Suna, idi bez mene.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okej, vidimo se.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Želiš nešto?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, jesi li htela nešto?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pismo?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Htela sam da ga dam Sunakavi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:24.14,SFX-BlackWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(393.333,51.334)}Suni?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.10,SFX-GrayWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(577.333,140)}Ne treba mi ništa zauzvrat, samo želim da me zavoliš
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.61,SFX-BlackWhite,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Za: Sunakavu\NNe treba mi čokolada zauzvrat. Samo želim da me zavoliš.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, pogrešno sam te procenio.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I izvini, video sam.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.04,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Znači to je devojka koja je slala Suni anonimna pisma sve vreme.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini što sam ti skvasio pismo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu je, napisaću ga ponovo{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.96,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dozvoli da ti se nekako izvinim!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci šta želiš!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.34,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro. Ako se setiš nečega što mogu da učinim, samo mi reci.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pozdrav!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.77,0:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Takeo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Takeo"?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.06,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Možeš li onda da me saslušaš sada?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.65,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dozvoli mi da ti ispričam o Sunakavi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,U-U redu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A, ti ne znaš ko sam ja, zar ne?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.95,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bili smo u istom odeljenju u vrtiću, u sakura grupi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam Amami Jukika.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amami Jukika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:40.71,SFX-GrayWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(222.667,32)}Ugh...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.46,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Ne moraš toliko da se napinješ da se setiš.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislim da se sećam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.97,SFX-GrayWhite,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1300,0)\pos(645.333,315.333)}Izmaglica
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Amami Jukika!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zašto ništa ne priča?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čeka pravi trenutak?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Da možda ja kažem nešto?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ni ja nisam najbolji u ovome.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ali hajde ipak da probam.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Udri svom snagom!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, ja se izvinjavam što sam takva.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne snalazim se da pričam sa dečacima.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i nekada, u vrtiću,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.54,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,dečaci su posipali pesak na sve strane iako su se devojčice tu igrale kuće.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Moguće da sam radio to.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Donosili su i bube i svašta nešto na časove.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To sam radio.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bili su blatnjavi od ranog jutra.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To bih bio ja.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Čarape su im bile prljave.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I to sam bio ja.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.35,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali Sunakava je bio drugačiji.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ostavljao je utisak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.98,SFX-BlueWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1173.333,30)}Utisak...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.31,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Često je čitao slikovnice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:37.73,SFX-BlueWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1169,78.667)}Utisak?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Čitala sam iste knjige koje je on čitao,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,kako bih shvatila šta mu se sviđa.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uvek je tako pažljivo jeo svoj ručak.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I bio je dobar u "između dve vatre"!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bio je jako spretan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uvek je ostajao do kraja.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislila sam da je baš neverovatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali samo jednom...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sunakava, izbačen si!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.09,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bila sam iza Sunakave, pa uopšte nisam videla da je lopta bačena.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.31,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Da je on skočio da je izbegne, mene bi udarila.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To liči na njega.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Posle toga...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ovaj, izvini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pogođen si zbog mene.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Samo sam mislio da bi bilo nezgodno da te udari u naočare.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.74,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tu sam ga baš, baš zavolela!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pa razumem.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.91,0:06:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To je bio zadnji put da smo direktno razgovarali.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisi pričala sa njime od onda?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To je bilo tipa u osnovnoj, zar ne?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,U vrtiću.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Vrtiću?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sada smo prvi srednje, znači pre deset godina.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Deset godina?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta si radila deset godina?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Posmatrala ga iz daleka.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokom školskih festivala...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,pa i kad se ništa nije dešavalo.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Posmatrala sam čitav njegov život.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.44,0:07:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Takođe sam skupljala informacije o njemu i pokušala da mu odredim sudbinu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ona je gatara?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali mogla si bar jednom da popričaš sa njime.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne mogu da pričam ni sa običnim dečacima!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako da pričam sa nekim ko mi se sviđa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa šta ćeš onda da uradiš?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne mogu ništa.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.54,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemam hrabrosti da pričam sa njim ili da mu izjavim svoja osećanja.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.13,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Od vrtića, kroz osnovnu, nižu srednju i višu srednju,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uvek sam osećala olakšanje kada bi odbio neku devojku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako ne može da bude moj,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.80,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,često pomislim kako onda ne želim da bude ičiji, ikada.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je li to kletva?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ipak, svaki put kada dođe Dan zaljubljenih,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.73,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,pomislim da bih mogla da mu izjavim ljubav.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.35,0:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali nikada nemam hrabrosti da napišem ime.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pošto nemam hrabrosti da popričam sa njim,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,uvek se šunjam negde oko njega.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deset godina... Neverovatno.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.49,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoja devojka, Jamato, izgleda kao fina osoba.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.25,SFX-GrayWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(212,20.667)}Otkud sad\Npomenu Jamato?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.91,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kada vidim kako ste vas dvoje srećni...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,baš vam zavidim.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.46,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Divno je kada postoje obostrana osećanja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.63,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ni ove godine nisam mogla da napišem ime,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.59,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,ali sam mislila da mu lično predam pismo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali na kraju sam ga samo nosala okolo celog meseca.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemam hrabrosti da mu ga predam.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.48,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunakava je uvek tako staložen i kul.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikad ne radi ništa uvrnuto.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije baš tako.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Radi i on razne nasumične stvari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.20,0:08:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pomislio sam da bi bilo zanimljivo da te zove "brother" na engleskom.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Istina.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kada je sa tobom, često se osmehuje.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Zavidim ti.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Volela bih da živim pored njega.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Onda bismo išli istim autobusom u vrtić,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.26,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,i mogli bismo da se kupamo zajedno.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mada mi to ne radimo više.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogli bismo i da se slikamo u kadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To nismo nikad radili!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jako dugo ti zavidim.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači. Izvini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.86,0:09:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali i meni je potreban Suna.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Istina je da je Suna kul.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, da.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeste.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno je savršen, idealan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idealan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, jeste on kul, ali je i običan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponekad se saplete.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Da ga nisi idealizovala?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.67,0:09:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam pomislila kako je on isti kao neki moj ideal.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.34,0:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On je postao ono što ja smatram idealom.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeo?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A, pa, vidiš...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.77,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nestala je!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ne, još osećam njeno prisustvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.60,SFX-GrayWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1072,12.666)}Zašto su ti\Npantalone mokre?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:48.60,SFX - WhiteBrown,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(106.666,38)}Pa...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.81,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nećeš kući?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A, da, hoću.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo kući.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš imaš velika stopala.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Take!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Odrastao si čovek više! Nemoj više da se prljaš tako!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nisam pomislila kako je on isti kao neki moj ideal.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.87,0:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On je postao ono što ja smatram idealom.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ništa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iznenađujuće puno je ima na njegovim slikama.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Suna, možda svi ljudi...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.93,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,u srcima imaju nešto nalik na jezgro od usijanog, istopljenog čelika,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,ali to ne pokazuju svetu, već samo žive tako,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,kao da se ništa ne dešava unutra.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.61,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.99,0:10:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mada možda i nisu svi takvi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.54,SFX-BlackWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,137.333)}U istoj smo\Nsrednjoj školi...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pa sad se ne kriješ?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.58,0:10:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, mislim da ću ipak pokušati da pričam sa Sunakavom.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I želim da mi ti pomogneš.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okej.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Smislila sam način da započnem razgovor na najprirodniji mogući način.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš li da ti ispričam?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.14,0:11:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.06,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogu li da te zamolim da se praviš da si se izgubio a da sam ti ja pomogla?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,U-U redu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To mu baš dođe izokola.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemam hrabrosti da mu izjavim ljubav,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.11,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ali želim bar jednom da mu priđem blizu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.53,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pošto njegov i moj svet nikada nisu imali dodirnih tačaka...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Razumem.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Možemo li večeras?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Suna ide do prodavnice otprilike jednom u tri dana.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, znam.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Suna!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Izgubio sam se na železničkoj stanici!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.35,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ova fina devojka mi je pomogla da se snađem.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.22,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš je ljubazna devojka.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Devojka?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš na Amami?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Idemo u iste škole još od vrtića.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.23,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A, tako znači.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Volim te.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Volim te, Sunakava!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.36,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne treba mi ništa zauzvrat, samo želim da me zavoliš!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.47,SFX - WhiteBrown,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,171.333)}Ljubav - Čežnja
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mislio sam da nemaš hrabrosti da mu kažeš.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pa, kako god,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ali zašto bežiš?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pazi!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta vriskaš!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislio sam da ćeš da padneš.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Bolje da sam pala.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da padnem da ohladim glavu!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.15,0:12:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo nije reka za hlađenje glave!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam planirala da mu kažem.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, i ja sam se iznenadio.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.24,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam mislila da će me se setiti.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali kada se setio,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,bila sam preplavljena osećanjima, morala sam.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, dobro, šta sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne možeš vratiti prosuto mleko.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.13,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne mogu li nekako da mu izbrišem sećanja?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.22,0:13:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Jok.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A nešto da kažem da mu zamažem oči?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Jok!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Jukika, jesi li srećna takvom izjavom?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ne želiš da mu kažeš lepo?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li misliš da si onime uspela da izraziš sva svoja dosadašnja osećanja?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ti nije žao da ne učiniš to kako treba?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Iz senke sam ga posmatrala zadnjih deset godina.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar neće misliti da sam odvratna?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,On ne bi nikada rekao tako nešto!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Reći ću mu kako se stvarno osećam.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Reći ću mu kako treba,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,i on će me lepo odbiti.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Završiću sa svime.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Još je tu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Amami,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.68,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,jesi li možda ti ta koja mi je ostavljala nepotpisane čokolade za Dan zaljubljenih?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Da si napisala ime, odgovorio bih ti.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Amami{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.07,0:14:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,da li me mrziš?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, pa nije da te mrzim.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ne?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Upravo tako.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.95,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne znaš dovoljno o meni da bi mogao da razviješ bilo kakva osećanja!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato ne želim tvoj odgovor sada!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:22.75,SFX-BlueBlue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1241.334,11.333)}Jukika?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato, molim te, saznaj više o meni!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakon toga ću saslušati tvoj odgovor!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tako znači.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stvari se mogu i tako postaviti,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.68,0:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ali opet si promenila priču od malopre, Jukika.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,U pravu si. Dobro, hajde tako.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Onda ću ti dati moj broj mobilnog.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.11,0:14:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Možeš bilo kada da me kontaktiraš.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.15,SFX-BlueWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(174.667,39.333)}Mada ponekad\Nneću moći\Nda se javim
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, hvala ti!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne moraš da budeš tako učtiva.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, idem ja onda.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kako sam mogla da učinim to?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sebe sam prestravila.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:06.17,SFX-BlueWhite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1118.667,18)}Bila si stvarno\Nubedljiva
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, i ja sam bio iznenađen.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali drago mi je zbog tebe.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Znači da ipak nije još gotovo.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Da...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ako ti se neko sviđao deset godina,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ne možeš tek tako da staviš tačku na to.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.43,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drago mi je što te nije odbio.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Suna, zašto je nisi odbio?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:30.28,SFX-RedBlack,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978.667,200.667)}Pritisak
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Da te nije ubedila?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, recimo.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recimo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:34.91,SFX - WhiteBrown,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,393)\pos(913.334,50)}Pilji...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Možda sam popustljiviji nego što sam mislio.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.03,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Možda?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A zašto si ti bio sa Amami?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bilo je ovako, pa tako, i onda eto.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.33,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uglavnom sam skapirao.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Izgleda da si bio dobar u "Između dve vatre".
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.88,0:15:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,U bežanju.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.92,0:15:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jukika mi je ispričala.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A, tako znači.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ne mogu da procenim o čemu razmišlja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.18,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.93,0:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ništa, samo sam se setio kako si ti igrao.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.73,0:16:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Samo si jurio najjače igrače.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:08.03,SFX-GrayWhite,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(903.99,59.64)}Na!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:08.03,SFX-GrayWhite,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(327.99,64.973)}Na!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.02,0:16:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Na kraju bi uvek bio u obračunu sa najjačim protivnikom.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i kada bi gađali nekoga drugog,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,ti bi skočio u stranu da uhvatiš loptu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:15.03,SignD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(612,0)\pos(1092.763,25.71)}Takeo!\NTakeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:15.03,SignD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(612,0)\pos(21.097,26.377)}Šingo!\NŠingo!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Na kraju to više i nije bila ista igra.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesam li stvarno?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.95,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi, jesi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tako znači.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suna stvarno dobro opaža stvari.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.75,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ali verovatno nije primetio taj trenutak kada se Jukika zaljubila u njega.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neću mu reći,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.22,0:16:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zato što je to nešto što će mu ona reći jednog dana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.06,SFX - WhiteBrown,,0,0,0,,{\pos(273.333,519.333)}Detektovano\Nprisustvo
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jukika je ovde!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeo?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ništa, ništa.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zašto ne priđe da popriča sa njime?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čeka priliku?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je li to?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.87,0:17:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dobro!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jukika, Suna ide ka tebi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:03.71,SFX-BrownWhite,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(1025.14,18.473)}Hvala
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Šta to radiš?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.29,0:17:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Suna, sačekaj tu na trenutak.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.00,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jukika...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tu si!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta vriskaš!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nisi htela da Suna sazna više o tebi?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Idi!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Neka sazna!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dobro!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Suna!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.02,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo je Jukika.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Prošetaj sa njom kući.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A, dobro.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li i ti živiš na ovu stranu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Srećno, Jukika.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nadam se da ćeš uspeti.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.08,0:17:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ha?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zašto stoji tako daleko od njega?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.62,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Amami živiš u susedstvu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.58,0:17:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.92,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A i danas baš hodaju polako.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sedam na voz ovde.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A ti, Amami?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro, vidimo se onda.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.05,0:18:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.14,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, zar nisi planirala da sazna više o tebi?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I..Izvinjavam se.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.06,0:18:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pored njega mi je bilo teško da se setim i da dišem, a kamoli nešto drugo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.86,0:18:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunakava je...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.53,0:18:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sunakava{\i0} je pričao sa mnom!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunakava...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Drži se, bre!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.45,SFX-GrayWhite,,0,0,0,,{\frz343.2\pos(1057.287,172.32)}Zgrab
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeo?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.04,0:18:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde si sada?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kod Šuei stanice.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta radiš?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.62,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.04,SignA,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934.86,183.53)}Devojka
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Devojka!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj trenutak.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.46,0:18:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, mogu li da objasnim Jamato šta se dešava?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne ide mi od ruke prikrivanje stvari i držanje tajni,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a i ne volim to da radim.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu je, reci joj.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Jamato?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.64,0:18:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Upravo sam pričao sa devojkom po imenu Jukika kojoj se sviđa Suna.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A, tako znači.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, je li u redu što si meni rekao?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Želela bih da me posavetuje!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoje objašnjenje je bilo lako za razumeti.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.62,0:19:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.53,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislio sam da ćeš pričati sa Sunom kao sa mnom i Jamato,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ali manje-više nisi ništa pričala sa njime.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoguće je.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jedva sam uspela da pričam sa njim a da me ne strefi šlog.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, razumem.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.67,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja sam bila jako nervozna kada sam prvi put pričala sa Takeom.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dok sam stajala ispred,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,nisam smela da stisnem zvonce, i samo sam stajala tako.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.68,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kada sam ga pozvala,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,srce mi je lupalo tako jako.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tako znači.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.77,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nisam znao ništa od toga tada,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.03,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ali stvarno sam imao sreće.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.37,0:19:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako ne možeš da pričaš sa njime, možda da se osmehuješ?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislim da ne umem lepo da se osmehujem.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A pisma i poruke?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.84,0:19:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako su anonimna, mogu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:06.60,Sunakawa,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,225)\fs40\pos(691.333,359)}Hmmmmm!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako da ti pomognem?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto ne bismo otišli negde zajedno?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To je zabavno samo po sebi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.85,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako je!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobra ideja, Takeo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Da izađem negde sa Sunakavom!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Suna!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li dobio neku poruku od Jukike?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.82,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A, evo upravo jednu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovde Amami.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.70,0:20:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti za danas.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li želiš da odemo u zoo vrt neki put?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gouda i Jamato mogu da pođu sa nama.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako želiš, reci mi koji datumi i koje vreme ti odgovara.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baš je formalna.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ti gledaš?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.13,0:20:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Piše da poziva i tebe i Jamato. Hoćeš da idemo?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.59,0:20:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Aha.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Može! Može!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš nešto?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.84,0:20:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.89,0:20:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, dobro.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo onda svi zajedno.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.93,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Svaka čast, Jukika.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.40,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Suna, da li se ti stvarno slažeš sa ovime?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa čime?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako ne želiš da ideš,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.94,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,u redu je da tako kažeš.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.57,0:21:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Najbitnija su tvoja osećanja.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.62,0:21:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Da mi se ne ide, ne bih išao.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Znači da ti se ide?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, valjda.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije to strava?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Možda.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja mogu kad god poželiš.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako joj reci.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rekao je da mu se ide.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Srećno, Jukika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:50.01,Title1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(965.333,548)}Pismo meni
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.09,0:22:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sledeći put: Pismo meni
